Stats
public static enum Stats.ExpiryEvent
extends java.lang.Enum<Stats.ExpiryEvent>

Possible events at which statistics fields can be considered expired. Each one refers to the start of the next occurrence of that event. For example, all fields with an expiry of ExpiryEvent.RUN will be cleared on the start of the next run.
